## Dual-Framework Parallel Execution

### Flow (Both Modes, Both Tabs)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["User selects 'Auto' framework"] --> B["AI ranks all frameworks by score"]
    B --> C{"len(rankings) >= 2?"}
    C -->|Yes| D["v1 = rankings[0], v2 = rankings[1]"]
    C -->|No| E["v1 = rankings[0] only"]
    D --> F["Create v1_dir/ & v2_dir/"]
    F --> G["Run v1 & v2 in parallel"]
    G --> H["ThreadPoolExecutor (Narrative)<br/>Thread + job dict (Review)"]
    H --> I["Wait for both to finish"]
```

